@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_btkejx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.72) / (v0 + 0.30 + tmp + 0.51)) + v2)
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.46 * tmp + 0.08)) - 0.64)
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.58) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.49)))
    v0 = 0.16
    v2 = wp.exp((tmp / 0.95))
    data[tid] = v0
